# 🎮 Game Hub

A full-stack item trading platform built for **Last Chaos** players. Players can list items for sale, buy items using in-app coins, and manage their wallet with PayPal integration. Admins can monitor and approve deposits, withdrawals, and detect fraud.

---

## 🚀 Features

- 🛒 **Item Marketplace** – Post, edit, delete, and browse trade listings
- 💰 **Coin Wallet** – Buy items with coins, deposit via PayPal, withdraw to PayPal or bank
- 🔐 **JWT Authentication** – User login/register with token storage
- 🧑‍💼 **Admin Dashboard** – Approve/reject transactions, view trade history, and fraud flags
- 📨 **Post-Purchase Messaging** – Contact seller after buying item

---

## 🧱 Tech Stack

| Frontend | Backend |
|----------|---------|
| React + Tailwind | Node.js + Express |
| Axios | MongoDB + Mongoose |
| React Router | Firebase (Auth/Storage) |
| Toastify + Lucide Icons | PayPal Payouts SDK |

